A homeless vigilante blows away crooked cops,pedophile Santas, and
other scumbags with his trusty pump-action shotgun. It&#x27;s as awesome as
it sounds. This movie has blood,guts,whores,bad guys and guns I mean
what more could you possibly want ? I loved every minute of this movie
I honestly think this is the best bloody movie I have ever seen. Maybe
I liked this movie so much because I love revenge,I liked movies like
payback and the punisher but I think this movie is better. Go see hobo
with a shotgun it&#x27;s got nudity,its got violence and gore it&#x27;s so
brutal. you will stay thrilled the entire movie. you don&#x27;t have to
think ... just relax and watch hobo with a shotgun shooting people.
heads are blown off and ripped off and smashed it&#x27;s so much fun I had a
blast this movie was great . However i seen many people get up and
leave during the film, and all I&#x27;m thinking in my head was that these
